            "title": "盤中速報 - 士電(1503)股價拉至漲停，漲停價237.0元，成交11,244張",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>士電(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1503:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1503\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1503-TW</a>)22日10:11上漲21.5元，股價漲停報237.0元，委買1張、委賣1,680張，成交11,244張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要業務為重電機械類。電器機器類。租賃類。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>士電(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1503:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1503\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1503-TW</a>)近5日股價上漲8.84%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲0.98%，股價漲幅表現優於大盤。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+5,207 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+4,679 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：-10 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：+538 張</li> <li>融資增減：+244 張</li> <li>融券增減：+30 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
