            "title": "盤中速報 - 嘉澤(3533)大漲7.14%，報1425元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>嘉澤(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3533:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3533\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3533-TW</a>)22日10:01股價上漲95元，報1425.0元，漲幅7.14%，成交888張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>嘉澤(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3533:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3533\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3533-TW</a>)所屬產業為電子零組件業，主要業務為連接器。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>近5日股價下跌4.32%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲0.98%，短期股價無明顯表現。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：-329 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-411 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：+154 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：-72 張</li> <li>融資增減：+5 張</li> <li>融券增減：-4 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
